flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 44: Vendor Fulfillment Workflow and Operational Updates

  Alert[Vendor receives new order alert]
  Decision{Accept order?}

  Reject[Reject order path]
  RejectNotify[Notify buyer and release reserved inventory]
  Accept[Accept order]
  PickPack[Pick, pack, quality check]
  Label[Generate shipping label]
  Assign3PL[Assign logistics partner]
  Pickup[3PL pickup]
  PickupFail[Pickup failed or delayed]
  Reassign[Reassign 3PL and reschedule pickup]
  Status[Real-time status updates]
  Realtime[WebSocket plus in-app updates]

  InvUpdate[Inventory decrement per variant]
  Signals[Trigger AI operational updates\nvelocity, ROP, opportunities]
  Notify[Notify buyer and vendor channels]

  Alert --> Decision
  Decision -- No --> Reject --> RejectNotify
  Decision -- Yes --> Accept --> PickPack --> Label --> Assign3PL --> Pickup

  Pickup -->|Success| Status
  Pickup -->|Failure| PickupFail --> Reassign --> Pickup

  Status --> Realtime --> InvUpdate --> Signals --> Notify
